sqlQuery: SELECT part.p_retailprice, part.p_type, part.p_brand FROM part WHERE part.p_type = 'SMALL BRUSHED BRASS';
SELECT part.p_mfgr, part.p_container, part.p_type FROM part WHERE part.p_container = 'SM DRUM';
SELECT orders.o_orderstatus, orders.o_orderkey, orders.o_orderdate FROM orders WHERE orders.o_orderdate = '1996-11-26';
SELECT part.p_type, part.p_partkey, part.p_container FROM part WHERE part.p_type = 'STANDARD POLISHED COPPER';
SELECT part.p_name, part.p_mfgr, part.p_partkey FROM part WHERE part.p_brand = 'Brand#53';
SELECT orders.o_shippriority, orders.o_custkey, orders.o_orderstatus FROM orders WHERE orders.o_orderdate = '1997-01-26';

SELECT part.p_container, part.p_mfgr, MAX(part.p_partkey + part.p_size) as agg_0 FROM part  WHERE part.p_type IN ('ECONOMY PLATED TIN', 'LARGE ANODIZED BRASS', 'ECONOMY BURNISHED BRASS', 'SMALL ANODIZED BRASS', 'ECONOMY BURNISHED STEEL') AND part.p_retailprice >= 1747.9975700513344 AND part.p_brand NOT LIKE '%B%rand#12%' AND part.p_container NOT LIKE '%PK%G%' AND part.p_mfgr = 'Manufacturer#4' AND part.p_brand NOT LIKE '%Brand#44%' AND part.p_size <= 12.802114348231378 AND part.p_partkey >= 4232255.891156545 AND part.p_mfgr = 'Manufacturer#4' AND (part.p_type LIKE '%LARGE%' OR part.p_type IN ('STANDARD BURNISHED COPPER', 'PROMO POLISHED STEEL', 'LARGE ANODIZED STEEL', 'ECONOMY BURNISHED STEEL', 'PROMO ANODIZED BRASS', 'SMALL ANODIZED COPPER') OR part.p_type NOT LIKE '%MEDIUM%') AND part.p_container LIKE '%CA%N%' AND part.p_name LIKE '%rosy%' GROUP BY part.p_container, part.p_mfgr HAVING MAX(part.p_partkey + part.p_size) != 10000025.99725925 ORDER BY part.p_container, part.p_mfgr LIMIT 1000;
SELECT part.p_brand, part.p_size, part.p_partkey FROM part WHERE part.p_container = 'JUMBO CASE';
SELECT lineitem.l_shipdate, lineitem.l_suppkey, lineitem.l_returnflag FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1992-10-10';
SELECT lineitem.l_suppkey, lineitem.l_shipinstruct, lineitem.l_discount FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_shipdate = '1994-11-28';

SELECT customer.c_mktsegment, COUNT(*) as agg_0, MAX(customer.c_acctbal + customer.c_nationkey) as agg_1, AVG(customer.c_acctbal + customer.c_custkey) as agg_2 FROM customer  WHERE customer.c_mktsegment NOT LIKE '%MACHIN%ERY%' AND customer.c_mktsegment LIKE '%FURNITURE%' AND (customer.c_nationkey >= 7.770105153596565 OR customer.c_nationkey >= 6.334953797145203 OR customer.c_nationkey <= 14.201175366402094) AND (customer.c_acctbal >= 1259.4250823000068 OR (customer.c_acctbal >= 6362.847081884141 AND customer.c_acctbal <= 3631.600927501004)) AND customer.c_custkey >= 7019187.704769794 AND customer.c_comment LIKE '%a%long%' GROUP BY customer.c_mktsegment HAVING MAX(customer.c_acctbal + customer.c_nationkey) >= 4510.548914642671 ORDER BY customer.c_mktsegment;
SELECT part.p_brand, part.p_name, part.p_size FROM part WHERE part.p_type = 'STANDARD POLISHED STEEL';
SELECT lineitem.l_commitdate, lineitem.l_linenumber, lineitem.l_shipmode FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_commitdate = '1994-07-21';

SELECT part.p_container, COUNT(*) as agg_0, MAX(partsupp.ps_availqty) as agg_1 FROM partsupp JOIN part ON partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey JOIN supplier ON partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey  WHERE supplier.s_comment NOT LIKE '%pending,%' AND partsupp.ps_suppkey <= 329290.288612262 AND part.p_mfgr NOT LIKE '%Manufacturer#5%' AND partsupp.ps_availqty <= 582.5027992589547 AND partsupp.ps_partkey >= 14390621.54807564 AND part.p_type = 'PROMO PLATED BRASS' AND part.p_type NOT LIKE '%NICKEL%' AND partsupp.ps_supplycost <= 83.62558224982439 AND (supplier.s_nationkey <= 14.297764212819395 OR (supplier.s_nationkey <= 2.1418708960535744 AND supplier.s_nationkey >= 13.160855634340281)) AND part.p_comment NOT LIKE '%t%h%' AND supplier.s_suppkey <= 634035.1995985147 AND part.p_brand IN ('Brand#42', 'Brand#25', 'Brand#43', 'Brand#21', 'Brand#53', 'Brand#15', 'Brand#22', 'Brand#35') AND part.p_container NOT LIKE '%BA%G%' GROUP BY part.p_container ORDER BY part.p_container;
SELECT part.p_retailprice, part.p_partkey, part.p_container FROM part WHERE part.p_container = 'WRAP BOX';
SELECT part.p_name, part.p_partkey, part.p_brand FROM part WHERE part.p_brand = 'Brand#34';
SELECT part.p_type, part.p_size, part.p_container FROM part WHERE part.p_type = 'PROMO PLATED TIN';
SELECT part.p_brand, part.p_container, part.p_size FROM part WHERE part.p_container = 'LG BAG';
SELECT part.p_mfgr, part.p_type, part.p_partkey FROM part WHERE part.p_type = 'LARGE BURNISHED STEEL';

SELECT part.p_container, part.p_brand, part.p_mfgr, MIN(part.p_size + part.p_partkey) as agg_0 FROM part  WHERE part.p_type IN ('STANDARD ANODIZED NICKEL', 'MEDIUM POLISHED NICKEL', 'ECONOMY BURNISHED STEEL', 'ECONOMY BURNISHED COPPER', 'MEDIUM BRUSHED NICKEL', 'ECONOMY POLISHED COPPER') AND part.p_mfgr IN ('Manufacturer#2', 'Manufacturer#5', 'Manufacturer#1', 'Manufacturer#3', 'Manufacturer#4') AND part.p_partkey <= 829161.5861995447 AND part.p_container LIKE '%JAR%' AND part.p_brand IN ('Brand#33', 'Brand#51', 'Brand#35', 'Brand#34', 'Brand#23', 'Brand#55', 'Brand#44', 'Brand#21', 'Brand#45') AND part.p_mfgr != 'Manufacturer#3' GROUP BY part.p_container, part.p_brand, part.p_mfgr ORDER BY part.p_container, part.p_brand, part.p_mfgr;
SELECT lineitem.l_suppkey, lineitem.l_quantity, lineitem.l_orderkey FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1998-09-23';

SELECT MAX(supplier.s_nationkey) as agg_0 FROM supplier JOIN partsupp ON supplier.s_suppkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey  WHERE supplier.s_comment NOT LIKE '%final,%' AND supplier.s_suppkey <= 6954.504809575909 AND supplier.s_nationkey <= 18.186315906507968 AND partsupp.ps_supplycost >= 154.01432872585355 AND partsupp.ps_partkey <= 1107318.4707956181 AND (partsupp.ps_suppkey <= 820400.6997654657 OR partsupp.ps_suppkey <= 479547.23649232695 OR partsupp.ps_suppkey <= 857826.4238859225) AND partsupp.ps_availqty >= 3367.2564347155403;
SELECT lineitem.l_discount, lineitem.l_linestatus, lineitem.l_comment FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1994-12-05';

SELECT lineitem.l_returnflag, lineitem.l_shipinstruct, lineitem.l_shipmode, COUNT(*) as agg_0, MIN(lineitem.l_quantity) as agg_1, SUM(lineitem.l_orderkey) as agg_2 FROM lineitem JOIN partsupp ON lineitem.l_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey AND lineitem.l_suppkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey  WHERE lineitem.l_partkey <= 17924942.126029603 AND lineitem.l_shipmode IN ('FOB', 'RAIL', 'REG AIR', 'SHIP', 'TRUCK', 'AIR', 'MAIL') AND partsupp.ps_partkey <= 7565931.33305026 AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct NOT LIKE '%TAKE%' AND lineitem.l_tax >= 0.005586965022393774 AND partsupp.ps_availqty <= 4772.2354026979765 AND lineitem.l_orderkey <= 109412492.28559189 AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct NOT LIKE '%CO%D%' AND lineitem.l_linenumber >= 1.0 AND lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1992-08-13' GROUP BY lineitem.l_returnflag, lineitem.l_shipinstruct, lineitem.l_shipmode ORDER BY lineitem.l_returnflag, lineitem.l_shipinstruct, lineitem.l_shipmode LIMIT 10;

SELECT part.p_type, SUM(part.p_size + part.p_retailprice) as agg_0, AVG(partsupp.ps_supplycost + supplier.s_acctbal) as agg_1, AVG(part.p_retailprice + partsupp.ps_availqty) as agg_2 FROM partsupp JOIN supplier ON partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey JOIN part ON partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey  WHERE part.p_partkey <= 2543508.820661512 AND part.p_brand != 'Brand#34' AND partsupp.ps_suppkey <= 217205.28312481754 AND part.p_brand LIKE '%Brand#31%' AND partsupp.ps_comment NOT LIKE '%x-ray%' AND supplier.s_suppkey <= 630928.3342667494 AND part.p_type LIKE '%ANODIZED%' GROUP BY part.p_type ORDER BY part.p_type;

SELECT customer.c_mktsegment, AVG(customer.c_custkey) as agg_0, MAX(customer.c_nationkey + customer.c_custkey) as agg_1, SUM(customer.c_acctbal) as agg_2 FROM customer  WHERE customer.c_custkey >= 14581094.459706964 AND customer.c_acctbal >= 9042.266157445483 GROUP BY customer.c_mktsegment ORDER BY customer.c_mktsegment;

SELECT customer.c_mktsegment, MAX(customer.c_acctbal + customer.c_custkey) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM customer  WHERE customer.c_mktsegment = 'FURNITURE' AND customer.c_custkey >= 3640930.4135790067 AND customer.c_nationkey <= 1.972497597386377 AND customer.c_acctbal >= 5707.171934177937 GROUP BY customer.c_mktsegment ORDER BY customer.c_mktsegment;
SELECT lineitem.l_linestatus, lineitem.l_partkey, lineitem.l_quantity FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_commitdate = '1995-07-11';
SELECT part.p_partkey, part.p_name, part.p_retailprice FROM part WHERE part.p_type = 'ECONOMY BRUSHED BRASS';
SELECT orders.o_orderpriority, orders.o_comment, orders.o_custkey FROM orders WHERE orders.o_orderdate = '1995-11-11';
SELECT part.p_comment, part.p_mfgr, part.p_type FROM part WHERE part.p_type = 'SMALL BURNISHED STEEL';

SELECT lineitem.l_shipdate, part.p_brand, lineitem.l_commitdate, COUNT(*) as agg_0, MIN(lineitem.l_linenumber) as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM part JOIN partsupp ON part.p_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey  WHERE part.p_type IN ('MEDIUM BRUSHED STEEL', 'PROMO PLATED NICKEL', 'ECONOMY ANODIZED STEEL', 'SMALL BURNISHED BRASS', 'ECONOMY ANODIZED NICKEL', 'LARGE ANODIZED BRASS', 'MEDIUM BURNISHED COPPER', 'ECONOMY PLATED BRASS') AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct NOT LIKE '%NONE%' AND lineitem.l_quantity <= 43.93405356349836 AND part.p_comment NOT LIKE '%s%lyly%' AND lineitem.l_returnflag IN ('A', 'N') AND part.p_brand LIKE '%Brand#51%' AND part.p_mfgr IN ('Manufacturer#3', 'Manufacturer#2', 'Manufacturer#1', 'Manufacturer#4') AND (partsupp.ps_partkey >= 16943991.956357416 OR partsupp.ps_supplycost >= 538.6876607445746) AND part.p_size >= 15.441142757468633 AND partsupp.ps_suppkey <= 668126.9353045695 AND partsupp.ps_availqty <= 1886.757535560178 AND part.p_mfgr IN ('Manufacturer#5', 'Manufacturer#2', 'Manufacturer#3', 'Manufacturer#1') AND part.p_container NOT LIKE '%MED%' AND part.p_name NOT LIKE '%lace%' AND partsupp.ps_comment NOT LIKE '%slyly.%' AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct LIKE '%RETURN%' AND part.p_partkey <= 16322247.826323554 GROUP BY lineitem.l_shipdate, part.p_brand, lineitem.l_commitdate HAVING MIN(lineitem.l_linenumber) != 3.0000653808698905 ORDER BY lineitem.l_shipdate, part.p_brand, lineitem.l_commitdate;
SELECT lineitem.l_shipinstruct, lineitem.l_quantity, lineitem.l_suppkey FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1995-05-01';

SELECT part.p_type, MIN(nation.n_nationkey) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM part JOIN partsupp ON part.p_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey JOIN supplier ON partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey JOIN orders ON lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey JOIN nation ON supplier.s_nationkey = nation.n_nationkey JOIN customer ON orders.o_custkey = customer.c_custkey  GROUP BY part.p_type ORDER BY part.p_type LIMIT 100;
SELECT lineitem.l_receiptdate, lineitem.l_suppkey, lineitem.l_extendedprice FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_commitdate = '1992-05-31';

SELECT lineitem.l_commitdate, COUNT(*) as agg_0, MIN(partsupp.ps_partkey) as agg_1, MAX(partsupp.ps_availqty) as agg_2 FROM lineitem JOIN partsupp ON lineitem.l_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey AND lineitem.l_suppkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey JOIN part ON partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey  WHERE part.p_container != 'LG PACK' AND lineitem.l_linestatus = 'O' AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct LIKE '%RETURN%' AND part.p_partkey >= 9825217.9021782 AND (lineitem.l_shipinstruct NOT LIKE '%I%N%' OR (lineitem.l_shipdate != '1994-09-12' AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct = 'COLLECT COD')) AND partsupp.ps_suppkey <= 538822.9261456741 AND part.p_type != 'ECONOMY POLISHED NICKEL' AND part.p_mfgr LIKE '%Manufa%cturer#3%' AND part.p_container LIKE '%BO%X%' AND lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1995-10-19' AND lineitem.l_returnflag = 'A' AND lineitem.l_discount <= 0.09650228835522123 AND partsupp.ps_supplycost <= 174.70385029008497 AND partsupp.ps_availqty <= 4573.170913703382 AND part.p_type LIKE '%POLISHED%' AND partsupp.ps_partkey <= 10647914.703139722 GROUP BY lineitem.l_commitdate ORDER BY lineitem.l_commitdate;

SELECT MIN(lineitem.l_discount) as agg_0 FROM lineitem  WHERE lineitem.l_returnflag = 'R' AND (lineitem.l_linestatus != 'F' OR lineitem.l_linestatus IN ('F') OR lineitem.l_linestatus IN ('F', 'O')) AND lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1996-05-23' AND lineitem.l_suppkey <= 38318.766337773784;

SELECT SUM(customer.c_custkey + customer.c_nationkey) as agg_0, SUM(customer.c_custkey) as agg_1, SUM(customer.c_nationkey + customer.c_acctbal) as agg_2 FROM customer  WHERE customer.c_comment LIKE '%along%side%' AND customer.c_acctbal <= 505.31286663018284 AND customer.c_nationkey <= 23.899635573378056 AND customer.c_mktsegment != 'HOUSEHOLD' AND customer.c_mktsegment IN ('FURNITURE') AND customer.c_custkey <= 9270713.712656237;
SELECT lineitem.l_shipmode, lineitem.l_linenumber, lineitem.l_returnflag FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1997-04-08';
SELECT part.p_size, part.p_brand, part.p_mfgr FROM part WHERE part.p_container = 'JUMBO CASE';

SELECT part.p_mfgr, part.p_container, COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM part  WHERE part.p_type IN ('STANDARD POLISHED BRASS', 'PROMO ANODIZED TIN', 'MEDIUM PLATED STEEL') AND part.p_container NOT LIKE '%CAS%E%' GROUP BY part.p_mfgr, part.p_container ORDER BY part.p_mfgr, part.p_container;
SELECT lineitem.l_returnflag, lineitem.l_shipmode, lineitem.l_shipinstruct FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1995-04-24';
SELECT part.p_name, part.p_mfgr, part.p_partkey FROM part WHERE part.p_brand = 'Brand#31';

SELECT MAX(lineitem.l_quantity + lineitem.l_extendedprice) as agg_0, AVG(lineitem.l_orderkey) as agg_1 FROM lineitem  WHERE (lineitem.l_shipinstruct LIKE '%NO%NE%' OR lineitem.l_shipdate != '1994-01-27' OR lineitem.l_shipinstruct = 'COLLECT COD') AND lineitem.l_suppkey >= 41454.735692821734 AND lineitem.l_shipmode LIKE '%RE%G%' AND lineitem.l_extendedprice >= 59577.518225215324 AND lineitem.l_returnflag IN ('R', 'N') AND lineitem.l_linestatus = 'O' AND lineitem.l_orderkey <= 80186384.03784469 AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct LIKE '%CO%LLECT%' AND lineitem.l_commitdate = '1996-03-14' AND lineitem.l_quantity >= 6.604195012168809 AND lineitem.l_shipmode IN ('RAIL', 'TRUCK', 'AIR', 'SHIP', 'FOB') AND (lineitem.l_discount >= 0.014008832320619634 OR lineitem.l_discount >= 0.006903086406362354 OR lineitem.l_discount >= 0.0777583999405405) AND lineitem.l_partkey <= 5963104.472849112 AND lineitem.l_tax >= 0.06351194462239676 AND (lineitem.l_receiptdate != '1998-01-07' OR lineitem.l_shipdate = '1997-07-17') AND lineitem.l_linenumber >= 1.0 AND lineitem.l_linestatus = 'O' LIMIT 10;

SELECT customer.c_mktsegment, MIN(customer.c_custkey) as agg_0 FROM customer  WHERE customer.c_mktsegment NOT LIKE '%MACHINERY%' AND customer.c_mktsegment IN ('AUTOMOBILE', 'BUILDING', 'MACHINERY') AND customer.c_acctbal >= 9324.860471375127 GROUP BY customer.c_mktsegment ORDER BY customer.c_mktsegment;

SELECT lineitem.l_shipmode, COUNT(*) as agg_0, SUM(lineitem.l_quantity + part.p_size) as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM part JOIN partsupp ON part.p_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey  WHERE lineitem.l_shipmode LIKE '%RAI%L%' AND partsupp.ps_suppkey <= 5547.755700928342 AND part.p_retailprice >= 1878.2223881518073 AND lineitem.l_quantity <= 25.940479772185107 AND lineitem.l_tax >= 0.03677922543117741 AND lineitem.l_shipmode NOT LIKE '%S%HIP%' AND part.p_name NOT LIKE '%firebrick%' AND part.p_type IN ('MEDIUM POLISHED COPPER', 'LARGE BRUSHED TIN', 'SMALL POLISHED NICKEL', 'LARGE BRUSHED COPPER', 'ECONOMY POLISHED NICKEL', 'SMALL BRUSHED COPPER', 'STANDARD BURNISHED STEEL', 'PROMO BRUSHED COPPER', 'ECONOMY BURNISHED COPPER', 'PROMO ANODIZED COPPER') AND partsupp.ps_availqty <= 1789.2806762210664 AND lineitem.l_commitdate = '1995-03-30' AND part.p_size <= 18.26364556838855 AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct NOT LIKE '%RE%TURN%' GROUP BY lineitem.l_shipmode ORDER BY lineitem.l_shipmode;

SELECT part.p_container, part.p_mfgr, COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM lineitem JOIN partsupp ON lineitem.l_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey AND lineitem.l_suppkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey JOIN orders ON lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey JOIN part ON partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey  WHERE partsupp.ps_supplycost <= 363.8332713867948 AND part.p_type IN ('LARGE ANODIZED TIN', 'ECONOMY BURNISHED NICKEL', 'PROMO BRUSHED BRASS', 'STANDARD BRUSHED BRASS', 'LARGE ANODIZED COPPER', 'SMALL PLATED TIN', 'LARGE BRUSHED BRASS', 'STANDARD BURNISHED BRASS') AND lineitem.l_extendedprice >= 24609.692266638922 AND (orders.o_orderdate = '1998-06-19' OR (orders.o_orderdate != '1997-12-13' AND orders.o_orderdate = '1995-03-15')) AND orders.o_orderpriority != '4-NOT SPECIFIED' AND (partsupp.ps_suppkey >= 720503.192928958 OR partsupp.ps_suppkey >= 521893.5353978793) AND (lineitem.l_linestatus = 'O' OR lineitem.l_linestatus IN ('F', 'O') OR lineitem.l_linestatus IN ('O', 'F')) AND orders.o_orderkey >= 70557452.76319848 AND part.p_container NOT LIKE '%WRAP%' AND partsupp.ps_availqty >= 7736.599490030978 AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct != 'TAKE BACK RETURN' AND orders.o_comment LIKE '%furio%usly.%' AND lineitem.l_suppkey <= 725818.8936058718 AND orders.o_shippriority <= 0.0 AND part.p_partkey >= 9803895.167484423 AND lineitem.l_linenumber <= 3.0 AND partsupp.ps_comment LIKE '%have%' AND partsupp.ps_partkey <= 17756719.07631371 AND part.p_retailprice >= 2000.8243935464855 GROUP BY part.p_container, part.p_mfgr ORDER BY part.p_container, part.p_mfgr;

SELECT part.p_brand, part.p_mfgr, part.p_container, AVG(partsupp.ps_partkey + part.p_retailprice) as agg_0, MIN(supplier.s_nationkey + partsupp.ps_availqty) as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM part JOIN partsupp ON part.p_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey JOIN supplier ON partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey  WHERE part.p_container NOT LIKE '%B%AG%' AND (part.p_brand != 'Brand#54' OR part.p_name NOT LIKE '%honeyd%ew%') AND partsupp.ps_partkey <= 6543354.365151927 AND (supplier.s_nationkey >= 3.607579515636247 OR (supplier.s_nationkey >= 18.638828078653106 AND supplier.s_nationkey >= 3.2704073146000057)) AND supplier.s_suppkey >= 766020.0625291917 AND part.p_type IN ('MEDIUM PLATED COPPER', 'STANDARD POLISHED COPPER', 'ECONOMY BURNISHED BRASS', 'LARGE BURNISHED TIN', 'SMALL PLATED STEEL') AND part.p_partkey <= 4601988.549849252 AND partsupp.ps_suppkey <= 815497.8093989398 GROUP BY part.p_brand, part.p_mfgr, part.p_container HAVING COUNT(*) >= 0 ORDER BY part.p_brand, part.p_mfgr, part.p_container;
SELECT lineitem.l_linenumber, lineitem.l_shipdate, lineitem.l_receiptdate FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1997-09-30';

SELECT lineitem.l_shipmode, lineitem.l_shipdate, MAX(lineitem.l_extendedprice + lineitem.l_linenumber) as agg_0 FROM part JOIN partsupp ON part.p_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey JOIN supplier ON partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey  WHERE lineitem.l_discount <= 0.08283089078676527 AND lineitem.l_shipdate = '1996-01-19' AND lineitem.l_shipmode IN ('TRUCK', 'REG AIR') AND part.p_name LIKE '%blac%k%' AND supplier.s_suppkey <= 411510.844998082 AND part.p_brand IN ('Brand#43', 'Brand#32', 'Brand#44', 'Brand#54', 'Brand#45', 'Brand#51', 'Brand#22', 'Brand#25', 'Brand#13', 'Brand#41') AND part.p_mfgr LIKE '%M%anufacturer#5%' AND lineitem.l_shipmode LIKE '%TRUCK%' GROUP BY lineitem.l_shipmode, lineitem.l_shipdate ORDER BY lineitem.l_shipmode, lineitem.l_shipdate;
SELECT lineitem.l_returnflag, lineitem.l_discount, lineitem.l_linenumber FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_commitdate = '1996-01-11';

SELECT AVG(customer.c_acctbal) as agg_0, AVG(customer.c_acctbal + customer.c_nationkey) as agg_1 FROM customer  WHERE customer.c_acctbal <= 3283.588570450959 AND customer.c_nationkey <= 1.891466009029735 AND customer.c_mktsegment NOT LIKE '%MACHINERY%' AND customer.c_mktsegment LIKE '%BUILDING%' AND customer.c_custkey <= 1305847.3386212983 LIMIT 10;

SELECT lineitem.l_shipinstruct, orders.o_orderpriority, AVG(lineitem.l_quantity + orders.o_totalprice) as agg_0, AVG(lineitem.l_tax) as agg_1, MIN(lineitem.l_linenumber) as agg_2 FROM lineitem JOIN orders ON lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey  WHERE lineitem.l_shipmode NOT LIKE '%FOB%' AND orders.o_orderstatus != 'F' AND orders.o_totalprice >= 148685.19976339984 AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct NOT LIKE '%NONE%' AND lineitem.l_tax >= 0.055662385420312814 AND lineitem.l_suppkey >= 976461.2275703691 AND (orders.o_orderpriority NOT LIKE '%4-NOT%' OR (orders.o_orderpriority LIKE '%1-URGENT%' AND orders.o_orderpriority NOT LIKE '%4-NO%T%')) AND orders.o_orderdate = '1995-12-17' AND (lineitem.l_partkey <= 18322815.410028506 OR (lineitem.l_quantity >= 49.1391161901332 AND lineitem.l_partkey <= 11438131.9831857)) AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct IN ('COLLECT COD') AND (orders.o_orderpriority = '3-MEDIUM' OR orders.o_custkey <= 11671494.246971939) AND (lineitem.l_linestatus != 'F' OR lineitem.l_returnflag = 'N') AND orders.o_comment LIKE '%sl%y%' AND orders.o_orderstatus = 'O' GROUP BY lineitem.l_shipinstruct, orders.o_orderpriority HAVING AVG(lineitem.l_quantity + orders.o_totalprice) <= 151146.62272065197 ORDER BY lineitem.l_shipinstruct, orders.o_orderpriority;
SELECT lineitem.l_quantity, lineitem.l_returnflag, lineitem.l_linestatus FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_shipdate = '1994-12-12';

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, AVG(partsupp.ps_partkey) as agg_1, MAX(part.p_retailprice) as agg_2 FROM part JOIN partsupp ON part.p_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey JOIN supplier ON partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey  WHERE partsupp.ps_comment NOT LIKE '%p%ending%' AND part.p_brand LIKE '%Bra%nd#52%' AND supplier.s_suppkey >= 104812.24049641413 AND part.p_retailprice >= 1360.4216846610452 AND part.p_mfgr LIKE '%Manufacturer#1%' AND partsupp.ps_partkey >= 18533114.428560562 AND supplier.s_nationkey >= 13.301771597310763 AND (partsupp.ps_supplycost <= 973.9390106487531 OR (partsupp.ps_supplycost <= 173.32296290054256 AND partsupp.ps_supplycost >= 63.67592777000282)) AND part.p_container NOT LIKE '%L%G%';
SELECT lineitem.l_receiptdate, lineitem.l_extendedprice, lineitem.l_shipdate FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_shipdate = '1997-10-31';
SELECT part.p_brand, part.p_retailprice, part.p_type FROM part WHERE part.p_container = 'SM PKG';

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, MAX(lineitem.l_partkey + lineitem.l_extendedprice) as agg_1 FROM partsupp JOIN part ON partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey  WHERE lineitem.l_returnflag IN ('N') AND part.p_brand != 'Brand#34' AND part.p_size >= 19.09941297560922 AND partsupp.ps_comment LIKE '%re%gular,%' AND lineitem.l_linenumber <= 1.0 AND partsupp.ps_suppkey >= 437947.38694172655 AND part.p_brand NOT LIKE '%Brand#2%3%' AND part.p_type = 'LARGE PLATED TIN' AND (lineitem.l_shipmode = 'MAIL' OR lineitem.l_comment NOT LIKE '%f%luffily%') AND lineitem.l_linestatus IN ('O') AND (lineitem.l_shipinstruct != 'DELIVER IN PERSON' OR lineitem.l_comment LIKE '%final%' OR lineitem.l_shipinstruct = 'DELIVER IN PERSON') AND partsupp.ps_partkey >= 3649250.013419387 AND lineitem.l_shipdate = '1992-02-21' AND lineitem.l_tax >= 0.07791032737564735 AND lineitem.l_extendedprice >= 11957.202063119035;

SELECT part.p_mfgr, MIN(supplier.s_nationkey) as agg_0 FROM supplier JOIN partsupp ON supplier.s_suppkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey JOIN nation ON supplier.s_nationkey = nation.n_nationkey JOIN region ON nation.n_regionkey = region.r_regionkey JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey JOIN part ON partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey JOIN orders ON lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey  WHERE part.p_type = 'STANDARD BRUSHED BRASS' AND supplier.s_suppkey >= 795685.9706602106 AND orders.o_comment NOT LIKE '%acc%ounts%' GROUP BY part.p_mfgr ORDER BY part.p_mfgr;
SELECT lineitem.l_shipmode, lineitem.l_quantity, lineitem.l_orderkey FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_shipdate = '1995-01-01';
SELECT part.p_container, part.p_brand, part.p_name FROM part WHERE part.p_type = 'LARGE PLATED COPPER';

SELECT orders.o_orderpriority, lineitem.l_shipdate, part.p_mfgr, MIN(supplier.s_acctbal + lineitem.l_suppkey) as agg_0, MAX(orders.o_custkey) as agg_1 FROM part JOIN partsupp ON part.p_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey JOIN orders ON lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey JOIN supplier ON partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey  WHERE partsupp.ps_comment NOT LIKE '%lo%se%' AND supplier.s_nationkey <= 0.24029429932583457 AND (orders.o_orderpriority LIKE '%3-MEDIUM%' OR orders.o_orderpriority LIKE '%1-URGENT%' OR orders.o_orderpriority IN ('5-LOW')) AND lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1994-01-04' AND part.p_mfgr IN ('Manufacturer#1', 'Manufacturer#2', 'Manufacturer#5') AND supplier.s_comment NOT LIKE '%court%s.%' AND part.p_size <= 35.2275031061279 AND partsupp.ps_availqty >= 6948.810216843591 AND part.p_type NOT LIKE '%BUR%NISHED%' AND lineitem.l_shipmode LIKE '%TR%UCK%' AND (lineitem.l_commitdate = '1997-07-30' OR lineitem.l_commitdate = '1995-06-24' OR lineitem.l_commitdate = '1993-11-04') AND orders.o_shippriority >= 0.0 AND (lineitem.l_shipinstruct LIKE '%PER%SON%' OR (lineitem.l_shipinstruct LIKE '%CO%D%' AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct LIKE '%COLLE%CT%')) AND (lineitem.l_linestatus != 'F' OR lineitem.l_partkey >= 15211013.959449554 OR lineitem.l_linestatus = 'O') AND orders.o_custkey <= 11040803.25445871 AND partsupp.ps_supplycost >= 614.8266408489972 AND part.p_brand = 'Brand#51' AND part.p_mfgr LIKE '%Manufacturer#4%' GROUP BY orders.o_orderpriority, lineitem.l_shipdate, part.p_mfgr ORDER BY orders.o_orderpriority, lineitem.l_shipdate, part.p_mfgr;

SELECT part.p_mfgr, MIN(partsupp.ps_supplycost) as agg_0, MIN(partsupp.ps_availqty) as agg_1, AVG(partsupp.ps_suppkey + part.p_partkey) as agg_2 FROM part JOIN partsupp ON part.p_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey  WHERE partsupp.ps_comment LIKE '%packages%' AND part.p_container IN ('MED CAN', 'JUMBO CAN', 'LG PACK', 'JUMBO BOX', 'MED DRUM', 'LG BAG', 'LG PKG', 'MED PKG', 'WRAP CASE', 'MED BAG') AND part.p_name LIKE '%magen%ta%' AND part.p_container != 'LG CASE' AND partsupp.ps_suppkey >= 672734.2593798533 AND partsupp.ps_partkey >= 4549465.737915334 AND part.p_brand LIKE '%Brand#51%' AND part.p_type LIKE '%TIN%' AND (partsupp.ps_availqty <= 1566.2675258532172 OR (partsupp.ps_availqty <= 878.5037907799647 AND partsupp.ps_availqty >= 8674.808684152069)) AND (part.p_mfgr = 'Manufacturer#4' OR (part.p_size <= 41.926214118000914 AND part.p_mfgr IN ('Manufacturer#4', 'Manufacturer#1'))) AND part.p_retailprice >= 1673.602091274385 AND part.p_comment LIKE '%sly%ly%' AND part.p_type NOT LIKE '%ECONOMY%' AND (part.p_brand NOT LIKE '%Brand#2%3%' OR part.p_partkey <= 8653019.280937083) AND part.p_mfgr NOT LIKE '%Manufa%cturer#3%' GROUP BY part.p_mfgr ORDER BY part.p_mfgr;
SELECT lineitem.l_partkey, lineitem.l_returnflag, lineitem.l_tax FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1998-02-18';
SELECT part.p_name, part.p_comment, part.p_brand FROM part WHERE part.p_brand = 'Brand#32';

SELECT part.p_mfgr, part.p_type, SUM(part.p_retailprice) as agg_0 FROM part JOIN partsupp ON part.p_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey  WHERE part.p_partkey >= 15948036.865991151 AND part.p_container != 'SM CAN' AND part.p_type LIKE '%LARGE%' AND (part.p_comment NOT LIKE '%u%se%' OR part.p_name NOT LIKE '%in%dian%') AND (partsupp.ps_partkey >= 6768476.6470013345 OR partsupp.ps_partkey <= 18968473.691105384) AND part.p_mfgr IN ('Manufacturer#3') AND partsupp.ps_supplycost <= 889.5537875862127 AND part.p_retailprice >= 1768.0944501345384 GROUP BY part.p_mfgr, part.p_type ORDER BY part.p_mfgr, part.p_type;
SELECT lineitem.l_shipdate, lineitem.l_returnflag, lineitem.l_suppkey FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_shipdate = '1995-12-11';

SELECT orders.o_orderpriority, COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM orders  WHERE orders.o_orderstatus IN ('F', 'O') AND (orders.o_shippriority >= 0.0 OR orders.o_shippriority >= 0.0) AND orders.o_orderpriority LIKE '%5-LOW%' AND orders.o_custkey <= 12474289.75933084 AND orders.o_orderstatus = 'F' AND orders.o_totalprice <= 117595.42620599267 AND orders.o_orderdate != '1995-03-13' AND orders.o_orderkey <= 9971201.23924404 AND orders.o_orderpriority IN ('4-NOT SPECIFIED', '1-URGENT', '3-MEDIUM') GROUP BY orders.o_orderpriority ORDER BY orders.o_orderpriority;
SELECT part.p_mfgr, part.p_brand, part.p_name FROM part WHERE part.p_type = 'ECONOMY BURNISHED NICKEL';
